ing: 1 (8 ounce) package PHILADELPHIA Cream Cheese, softened
1 (10 ounce) can RO*TEL Diced Tomatoes and Green Chilies, drained
1 cup KRAFT Mexican Style Finely Shredded Four Cheese
des: "Black beans, spicy diced tomatoes, and shredded cheese on a base of cream cheese make a crowd-pleasing dip for chips and fresh veggies."
ins:
Spread cream cheese onto bottom of shallow dish.
Top with remaining ingredients.
